<para style="q1">

<verse number="21" style="v" />Evil will kill the wicked.</para>

<para style="q1">Those who hate the righteous will be condemned.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="22" style="v" />Yahweh rescues the lives of his servants.</para>

<para style="q1">None of those who take refuge in him will be condemned.</para>
